---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Medical Marijuana for Seniors in Florida | Releaf MD" 
  description="Discover the steps and benefits of getting a medical marijuana card for seniors in Florida. Safe clinical guidance by Dr. Kelly Ennix King."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        👵 Senior Wellness Guide
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Medical Marijuana for Seniors in Florida</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Safe, professional guidance for older adults exploring cannabis for pain, arthritis, insomnia, and quality of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Why More Florida Seniors are Choosing Medical Cannabis</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Seniors are currently the fastest-growing demographic of medical marijuana registry patients in Florida. As we age, managing chronic conditions like osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, neuropathy, insomnia, and general chronic pain often leads to complex pharmaceutical regimens. Medical cannabis offers a natural, plant-based alternative that can help improve mobility and sleep quality under proper clinical supervision.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">How to Get a Medical Marijuana Card for Seniors in Florida</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Getting certified is straightforward, and our staff at Releaf MD guides you through the state portal forms:
        </p>

        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Physician Assessment:</strong> Schedule your in-person evaluation with Dr. Kelly Ennix King. She reviews your current prescriptions to check for potential drug interactions and discusses safe ways to consume cannabis.</li>
          <li><strong>State Application Support:</strong> We help seniors upload their photo and submit their registry application fee ($75) online.</li>
          <li><strong>Dosing Guidance:</strong> We construct a personalized plan detailing low-THC and CBD options so you can experience relief without feeling disoriented.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 my-8">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Non-Smokable Dosing Alternatives</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            Many seniors are hesitant to try medical cannabis because they do not want to smoke. Dr. Kelly specializes in prescribing non-smokable alternatives such as sublingual tinctures (drops under the tongue), oral capsules, topical creams for localized joint pain, and transdermal patches.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Safety and Drug Interactions</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Patient safety is our primary focus. During your session, Dr. Kelly will look closely at any medications you take for blood pressure, blood thinners, or diabetes, as cannabinoids can occasionally alter how these drugs are metabolized by the liver. Having a clinical physician oversee your cannabis use ensures your safety and peace of mind.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
